Reservation mgmt
issue.body:
What does this do? Let's see:
- Adds a view for an agency to manage its day's reservations
- Those reservations which are no `CHECKEDIN` have actions available
- Can Check-In the reservation, updating the reservation
- OR can cancel a reservation, freeing up space
- Updates the card on the dashboard to tie reservations to query data
- Even adds fancy reloading effects to GMaps when changing how many beds you want to search for or how distant you want to search out
- Adds links to the sidebar
- Cleans up a lot of UI stuff
- Ensures Charlie had something pretty decently cool to contribute 🎉 🌮 

@adubbs
